OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774598699
OL,3,CTransgender women athletes banned from
OL,4,Ccompeting in female Olympic events
OL,6,FTransgender women athletes are now
OL,7,Fexcluded from the Olympics due to a
OL,8,Fnew eligibility policy agreed upon on
OL,9,FThursday.
OL,11,FThe policy, accepted by the
OL,12,FInternational Olympic Committee (IOC)
OL,13,Faligns with US President Donald
OL,14,FTrump's executive order on women's
OL,15,Fsports and comes ahead of the 2028 Los
OL,16,FAngeles Games.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774598699
OL,3,CTransgender women athletes banned from
OL,4,Ccompeting in female Olympic events
OL,6,F"Eligibility for any female category
OL,7,Fevent at the Olympic Games or any
OL,8,Fother IOC event, including individual
OL,9,Fand team sports, is now limited to
OL,10,Fbiological females," the International
OL,11,FOlympic Committee said.
OL,13,FIt added that eligibility would be
OL,14,Fdetermined "on the basis of a onetime
OL,15,FSRY gene screening," a method used to
OL,16,Fcheck for the presence of a Y
OL,17,Fchromosome.
OL,19,FIt is unclear how many, if any,
OL,20,Ftransgender women are competing at an
OL,21,FOlympic level.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,317,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774598699
OL,3,CTransgender women athletes banned from
OL,4,Ccompeting in female Olympic events
OL,6,FNo woman who transitioned from being
OL,7,Fborn male competed at the 2024 Paris
OL,8,FSummer Games.
OL,10,FThe eligibility policy "protects
OL,11,Ffairness, safety and integrity in the
OL,12,Ffemale category," the IOC said.
OL,14,F"It is not retroactive and does not
OL,15,Fapply to any grassroots or
OL,16,Frecreational sports programs," said
OL,17,Fthe IOC, whose Olympic Charter states
OL,18,Fthat access to play sport is a human
OL,19,Fright.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
