PN,31604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774598699
OL,3,CTransgender women athletes banned from
OL,4,Ccompeting in female Olympic events
OL,6,FAfter an executive board meeting, the
OL,7,FInternational Olympic Committee
OL,8,Fpublished a 10-page policy document
OL,9,Fwhich also restricts female athletes
OL,10,Fsuch as two-time Olympic champion
OL,11,Frunner Caster Semenya with medical
OL,12,Fconditions known as differences in sex
OL,13,Fdevelopment, or DSD.
OL,15,FSpeaking in a video on the social
OL,16,Fmedia site X, IOC president Kirsty
OL,17,FCoventry said: "Today, we the
OL,18,FInternational Olympic Committee have
OL,19,Fpublished a policy on the protection
OL,20,Fof the female category.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
