PN,31605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1774598699
OL,3,CTransgender women athletes banned from
OL,4,Ccompeting in female Olympic events
OL,6,F"I understand that this is a very
OL,7,Fsensitive topic. As a former athlete,
OL,8,FI passionately believe in the rights
OL,9,Fof all Olympians to take part in fair
OL,10,Fcompetition.
OL,12,F"The policy that we have announced is
OL,13,Fbased on science and it has been led
OL,14,Fby medical experts with the best
OL,15,Finterests of athletes at its heart.
OL,16,FThe scientific evidence is very clear
OL,17,F` male chromosomes give performance
OL,18,Fadvantages in sports that rely on
OL,19,Fstrength, power or endurance."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
